Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:38.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm breaking up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:41.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go out with someone like you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:43.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking up...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:45.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:46.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:48.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani and I are breaking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:51.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Owww!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:01:54.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like that is the very reason Otani is fed up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:58.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, what the heck were you thinking, leaving your studying boyfriend behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:00.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,and going out with another guy at the drop of a hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:02.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:04.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Was my account inaccurate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:05.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:09.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:12.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care. You reap what you sow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:13.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Figure it out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:15.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:16.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right. Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep apologizing,\N I'm sure he'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:24.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to cheat on him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,that really was the wrong thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:31.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a limit to my stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:37.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:39.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for going out with that other guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to do anything that stupid ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:43.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:46.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go out as much you want. It's got nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:49.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:50.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:54.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't break up with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! A man never goes back on his word.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:57.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:02:58.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There s no need to act all macho now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This only happened because you did something you shouldn't have, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:02.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm apologizing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things that can be fixed with an apology, and things that can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:07.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a stranger to me from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:13.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:18.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:20.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:22.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:25.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:29.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening... \NThis is all a dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:32.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Its been a while since that last happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:42.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:47.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:50.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:54.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's really over, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:57.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi, I'm sorry I said such cruel things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:00.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The whispering of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:03.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you asked me to come here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home! I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:06.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:08.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really going to break up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:10.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,For how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:11.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "for how long"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,For good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,FOLEVER!{This is deliberate}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:20.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:24.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Your future doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:26.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm breaking up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I worry about her so much that I can't concentrate on my studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:31.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:34.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you break up, won't you still worry about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all! I don't care anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:37.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally relaxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:46.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think he was that stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:49.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. It was all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this is an important time for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't bother him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're just going to leave it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:57.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:01.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who helped me with the Hokkaido problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:04.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:08.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, but it's okay. Things are already over between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:19.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to give this to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:27.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the time to make it, so it's still okay to give it to him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani, do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:45.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:49.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:52.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A-chan, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:53.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:57.89,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz272.26\pos(278,305)\fscx85\fscy121.25\4c&H9FD2D7&\3c&HAAE1E6&\c&H1E2E36&}Otani Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:58.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:08.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani Atsushi-sama, I support you in your test efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:12.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's from Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:17.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice! It looks really warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it on, A-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:21.65,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(359,39)}Do your best! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.40,TS,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(371,49)}PASS! OTANI FOR LIFE!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Recycled, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:34.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa-chan sure is a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:37.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But why didn't she come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:45.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Otani accepted my support goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:47.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-san, are you getting off now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're still working, Kohori-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the boss asked for your availability for{in} December.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,December...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:24.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be all alone this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-san, do you want to come in to work on Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:32.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all going to get together and have a party after we close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:34.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come too, Koizumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:34.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:35.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:37.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsubara-san will be there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:40.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the old lady got really drunk last year and went completely wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:41.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:43.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kohori-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about "the old lady"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:48.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:49.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking out the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:51.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you re looking for Koizumi-san, she already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just on my way home from prep school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys already broke up, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are short. How tall are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:20.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 158cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No way! I'm 2cm shorter than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:28.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! What did you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:30.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb with me. This is all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:33.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking Koizumi while she was asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only because she looked so beautiful while she was sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good Lord! Don't say something so embarrassing out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not embarrassing! It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Cram it, you midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 2cm taller than you, aren't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:51.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?! And besides, just what do you want with Koizumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:52.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:58.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to hold back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:04.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,F O R E
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,F O R E V
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:09.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what he did with the coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:13.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't matter. As long as he does his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A Christmas without Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Koizumi Risa, and I'll be singing an Umibouzu song!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped~ Can't be helped~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:29.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped~ Can't be helped~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:30.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:32.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I'm having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where Otani would usually break in and interject.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:41.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd always make a silly face and shout "Yeah!" right around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:44.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:47.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A-chan, want some Christmas cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:56.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You look really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You should take a break once in a while, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:03.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Christmas, after all. Why don't you spend it with Risa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:04.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:04.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:09.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw her near the station not long ago. She was with a boy around your height.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:12.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to hold back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:30.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could go on being normal without Otani,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,but I just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:34.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:39.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That looked painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:40.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:42.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Owww...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:47.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just no good without Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:04.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure fall over a lot for someone with such a big body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That coat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:11.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too sure about the recycled aspect of it, but thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:17.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you finish with your exams, I'm going to ask you out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm persistent, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:25.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you dump me, or say you're breaking  up with me, I'm not going to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:28.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So just focus on the entrance exams for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:44.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:45.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that I said we'd break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:48.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:51.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... your exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no. This is bod.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:54.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:12:01.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I seem to like you more than I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:03.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:05.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make weird noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:09.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to say something that nice to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if we break up a hundred times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is staring at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:22.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face might be hidden,\N but everyone can see mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:26.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. I've got "do your best"\N written on my back, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:29.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You really should do your best...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:33.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,1...2...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,, Oh... I didn't get you a Christmas present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:46.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But you already gave me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:48.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I didn't give you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It was something wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:55.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to like you more than I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:59.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the best present ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:19.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, we overcame that unprecedented crisis and entered the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's New Years Day, and we're already late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:29.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I only slept in because you called and woke me up at some odd hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:31.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be sad if I hadn't, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:32.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who says?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:36.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are both late, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:40.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone, the lovey-dovey couple is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:42.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on getting back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this was my chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:50.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pray for them to break up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:53.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka-senpai is being petty as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:14:02.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani and the others started seriously getting into pre-exam study,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:06.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,and Nobu-chan and I prayed for them from the sidelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to hit the sales!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:12.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan, this'll go really well with that skirt you bought last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:21.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else is working so hard. Is it okay for us to be doing stuff like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:24.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Not "us". You're the only one who still hasn't decided on your future plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What course are you going to take at technical college?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:30.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are so many...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:34.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, if Otani is going to be a teacher, how about I become a kindergarten teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll need to take an exam to get into a college specializing in early childhood education.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:41.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what about going into fashion design? You've got a good sense of style.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:46.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do like looking nice... but this and that are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Darling, I m on my way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:53.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiharu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:02.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:03.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,, Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:03.83,alt,,0000,0000,0000,, Huh?!{overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}The Center Test is an annual standardized test offered throughout Japan and is used by many universities to determine admission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun failed the Center Test?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:09.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you and Chiharu-chan won't be able to go to the same school!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sick the day of the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:22.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He took too much cold medicine and couldn't remember anything from about halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So... that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:28.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go to the same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:31.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for breaking my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Suzuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:38.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him alone for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:49.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, last year we decided to visit a University and went to their festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:55.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come have some fun with us? What year are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... I'm still a high school senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:02.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you going to apply here next year?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:06.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be great having a cute girl like you come to our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:09.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:11.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:13.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What? She s already got a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:13.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,University is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots and lots of guys came...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:22.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So many... There were so many...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:24.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who... Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:25.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:27.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be by your side, Tanaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:29.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiharu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:50.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:55.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go to whichever school you go to, so do your best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:56.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:16:59.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,, Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:00.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Get what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to give up on your first choice school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:07.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I want to be with you, Suzuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:11.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:15.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you lower yourself to my level and change your first-choice university,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I can get in anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:20.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Suzuki-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:22.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,When Chiharu-chan is willing too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:26.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why would you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't keep our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:34.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there are plenty of other guys who could protect you at university in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:41.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tanaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chiharu-chan, that's dangerou-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:44.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:45.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:51.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go to the same school just so you can protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:56.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:58.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you say I can replace you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiharu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying you re not confident...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:08.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun, you're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chiharu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She got pretty angry, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:21.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She was really upset...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:23.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:24.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:27.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it have to be like that? \NCan't you two just go to the same school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:32.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for her own good, and for my good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see it. That book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:45.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a literature professor who Tanaka-san really respects teaching at that university.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:49.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So to give up her first-choice school for my sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:54.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I think when she works out what she really wants to do in the future, she'll regret not going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:56.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:58.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So you said those things deliberately, Suzuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:04.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you try to act cool like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:07.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's completely the wrong way to show her you care about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:10.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Why not just tell her the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:13.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She would've been much happier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:16.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:16.80,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go.{overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:55.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:58.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You were being considerate of me to that extent...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:00.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I never realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:08.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to keep studying, and get into the same school as you next year,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:10.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,so please wait for me until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:20.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Chiharu-chan, Suzuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.13,0:20:27.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You've been sighing for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:32.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:35.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm the only one who hasn't decided on anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:36.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:40.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,After watching those two today, I realized I really need to decide now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:44.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,so that when I work out what I really want to do in the future, I won't have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Work that brain of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:51.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll need to get yours into gear too for your exam prep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:58.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So time passed quickly, and now the entrance exams are already tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:05.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! What the heck am I thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:15.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:16.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:20.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This house has been infected by a level 5 virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:23.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Level...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:25.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on?! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's influenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:30.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:33.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father and sister are both feverish and sick too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This house is under quarantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:36.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Quarantine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:38.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:40.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an exam tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:42.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:43.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:45.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry. Take that and flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:47.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and stay at a healthy friend's house for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:50.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:54.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani, I'm praying for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:59.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait... I have an exam tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:02.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:04.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:27.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best in the exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:29.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's already time for graduation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:30.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi, this isn't the time to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:33.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,, We're going to be late for graduation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:35.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely Complex~ LoveCom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:37.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Final Episode: Together Forever.
